Package gameClient

Class CL_Agent

java.lang.Object
gameClient.CL_Agent
public class CL_Agent
extends java.lang.Object
This class represents the agents in the game. The agent rule is to collect all the pokemon in the game. Each agent has: speed - which represents the speed of the agent. The speed is changed according to the number of pokemon who eats, the greater the value, the greater the speed. pos - which represents the position of the agent in the graph. currEdge - which represents the current agent's edge. currNode - which represents the current agent's node. value - which represents the agent's value, which sums the value of tall the pokemon that the agent ate. targetPokemonsList - which contains the ID of all the pokemon that the agent is chasing.
